com.linecorp.armeria.client.circuitbreaker.metrics

Class DropwizardMetricsCircuitBreakerListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.linecorp.armeria.client.circuitbreaker.metrics.DropwizardMetricsCircuitBreakerListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CircuitBreakerListener

    public final class DropwizardMetricsCircuitBreakerListener
extends Object
implements CircuitBreakerListener
    A CircuitBreakerListener which monitors the status of CircuitBreakers using dropwizard metrics.

    This class will generate the following metrics.

    metric namedescription
    {prefix}.{circuit-breaker-name}.transitions.closed The number of times that the circuit state has changed to CLOSED.
    {prefix}.{circuit-breaker-name}.transitions.open The number of times that the circuit state has changed to OPEN.
    {prefix}.{circuit-breaker-name}.transitions.halfopen The number of times that the circuit state has changed to HALF_OPEN.
    {prefix}.{circuit-breaker-name}.requests.rejected The number of requests that is rejected by the circuit breaker.
    {prefix}.{circuit-breaker-name}.counter.rate.success The rate of success requests in the counter time window.
    {prefix}.{circuit-breaker-name}.counter.rate.failure The rate of failed requests in the counter time window.
    {prefix}.{circuit-breaker-name}.counter.count.success The count of success requests in the counter time window.
    {prefix}.{circuit-breaker-name}.counter.count.failure The count of failed requests in the counter time window.
